data.description: Welcome to a  charming 2-story historic home iwithin walking distance of Colgate University. As you enter through the side porch, you'll be greeted to  the heart of the home. You'll find a spacious kitchen that seamlessly flows into a cathedral-ceiling family room, complete with a cozy wood-burning fireplace. A wall of windows and an atrium door lead to a deck and a private yard, creating a perfect spot for outdoor gatherings and relaxation.  You will discover a versatile space that  serves as a dining room and  a living room, with an additional room featuring a half bath. This extra room could easily be transformed into an office or an additional bedroom to suit your needs. Upstairs, the home boasts three comfortable bedrooms and a full bathroom, ensuring plenty of space for family and guests. The basement provides ample room for storage and features updated systems to give you peace of mind. The property  includes a two-story garage, offering room for two cars.  The large office space upstairs in the garage provides an excellent opportunity for remote work or creative pursuits. Don't miss  this lovely home and start enjoying the vibrant Village of Hamilton.
